  <brief_title>An Extension Study of Telbivudine, Lamivudine or Telbivudine Plus Lamivudine in Patients With Chronic Hepatitis B</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase IIb Extension Study of LdT (Telbivudine), Lamivudine or LdT Plus Lamivudine in Patients With Chronic Hepatitis B Who Have Completed Study NV-02B-003</official_title>
  <sponsors>
